# LaTeX build artifacts. The PDF is regenerated by `make` and not
# checked into the repo; arxiv accepts the .tex + .bib + figures
# directly and builds the PDF on its end.

*.pdf
*.aux
*.bbl
*.blg
*.log
*.out
*.toc
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk
*.synctex.gz

# Figure pipeline outputs (scripts/render_figures.py) — these ARE
# tracked: SVG/PDF are diffable text, PNG is the deck embed.
!figures/**/*.pdf
!figures/**/*.png
!figures/**/*.svg

# Editor / OS noise.
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
